snippet.title: KZ x PM - The Pokemon Brilliant Diamond Nuzlocke - Episode 03
snippet.description:
In this exciting episode of the Nuzlocke, we fight Roark and I know this because he's in the thumbnail. I am definitely not delirious writing this description at 5AM over a week before this video premieres.
